<P>AS IT IS ACTED AT THE THEATRE-ROYAL, DRURY-LANE.</P>
<P>THE SECOND EDITION.</P>
<P>BY THOMAS HOLCROFT.</P>
<P>LONDON: PRINTED FOR G. G. AND J. ROBINSON, PATERNOSTER ROW.</P>
